S.FORM: Si Raditya Adi (nianak nen 4 Agosto 2000) et sakey ya Indonesian ya rapper, managsulat na kansion tan managgaway plaka. Ginmapo si Raditya Adi ed karera to ed musika nen 2022 diad impaway to so sankaunaan ya single to ya say titulo to et "Orang Miskin".
